verbose_text: In comparison with the cells treated with the NC plasmid, the cells treated with the let-7d mimic showed significantly reduced mRNA and protein expression of ATG16L1 (P < 0.05), while the cells treated with the let-7d inhibitor presented significantly increased mRNA and protein expression of ATG16L1 (P < 0.05; XREF_FIG), suggesting that let-7d inhibited the expression of ATG16L1.
